<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qt3dcore-qcoresettings.xml">QCoreSettings</db:link> component should be set as a component of the scene root entity (although it could be anywhere in the scene graph). There should be a single instance.</db:para>
<db:para>It can be used to control some of Qt 3D's behavior.</db:para>
</db:section>
